  <p class="about_p">AntConc is free corpus analysis software that can be <a href="http://www.laurenceanthony.net/software/antconc/">downloaded for Windows, Mac, and Linux.</a> Using AntCont, it is possible to investigate concordances in your text, without having any coding knowledge.</p> 
